## ğŸŸ¢ **LEVEL 1: BASIC COMMANDS**

| Command | Kya Karta Hai | Syntax | Example |
|---------|---------------|--------|---------|
| `claude` | Claude Code start | `claude` | `cd project && claude` |
| `/exit` | Quit Claude | `/exit` | `/exit` |
| `/quit` | Exit (alternative) | `/quit` | `/quit` |
| `/help` | Commands list | `/help` | `/help` |
| `/reset` | Clear history | `/reset` | `/reset` |
| `/clear` | Clear screen | `/clear` | `/clear` |
| `Ctrl+C` | Force exit | `Ctrl+C` (2x) | Press twice |
| `Ctrl+L` | Clear screen | `Ctrl+L` | Press once |

---

## ğŸŸ¡ **LEVEL 2: FILE COMMANDS**

| Command | Kya Karta Hai | Syntax | Example |
|---------|---------------|--------|---------|
| `/new` | Create file | `/new <file>` | `/new app.js` |
| `/edit` | Edit file | `/edit <file>` | `/edit index.html` |
| `/read` | View file | `/read <file>` | `/read package.json` |
| `/delete` | Remove file | `/delete <file>` | `/delete test.js` |
| `/list` | Show files | `/list` | `/list` |
| `/ls` | List files | `/ls` | `/ls` |
| `/tree` | Folder structure | `/tree` | `/tree` |
| `/save` | Save changes | `/save` | `/save` |
| `/rename` | Rename file | `/rename <old> <new>` | `/rename app.js main.js` |
| `/move` | Move file | `/move <file> <path>` | `/move app.js src/` |
| `/copy` | Copy file | `/copy <src> <dst>` | `/copy app.js backup.js` |

