## ğŸ’¡ **QUICK COMMAND COMBINATIONS**

### **Full Workflow:**
```bash
/init react                    # Setup
/install axios tailwindcss     # Dependencies
/new src/App.jsx              # Create
/run                          # Test
/build                        # Build
/deploy vercel                # Deploy
```

### **Git Workflow:**
```bash
/git init                     # Initialize
/git add .                    # Stage
/commit "Initial commit"      # Commit
/git remote add origin URL    # Add remote
/push                         # Push
```

### **Code Quality:**
```bash
/lint                         # Check errors
/format                       # Format code
/analyze                      # Find issues
/optimize app.js              # Improve
/review                       # Full review
```

